  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlist The Game Today!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/43f7b1591d0b2c976844cf3f586dd864.poster.avif?t=1744765111\" width=670 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/43f7b1591d0b2c976844cf3f586dd864.webm?t=1744765111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/43f7b1591d0b2c976844cf3f586dd864.mp4?t=1744765111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/4c4a539352f2e6832d5605f2dba14695.avif?t=1744765111\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every note you play adapts to your actions, creating a unique symphony each time. The game turns your gameplay into a spontaneous musical masterpiece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Procedural musical puzzles that keep things fresh</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Harmonious compositions that sound great every time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No combat, no timers, just pure chill</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/1900919cf1a1da34fd3f45802f7750d8.poster.avif?t=1744765111\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/1900919cf1a1da34fd3f45802f7750d8.webm?t=1744765111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LightBreak is a unique musical journey that blends puzzle-solving with storytelling. As Ava, you'll use the mystical Saaz to create melodies that shape the world around you. From intricate 2D puzzles to immersive 3D environments, every aspect of the game pulses with music, creating a harmonious blend of gameplay and narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/1ca1099f9cea105fdb672ce4070e5272.poster.avif?t=1744765111\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/1ca1099f9cea105fdb672ce4070e5272.webm?t=1744765111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/f182ac6e6ddb5bb5b19713280e211f9c.avif?t=1744765111\" width=616 height=88 /></span>Dive into Ava's silent world, where only music can tell Ava's story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Uncover a rich story about ancient artifacts, adventure, and family</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Enjoy a soundtrack that feels like a musical canvas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve musical puzzles to reveal hidden messages</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/39d0c0360abc7a47b184f3aa9a4e6e53.poster.avif?t=1744765111\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/39d0c0360abc7a47b184f3aa9a4e6e53.webm?t=1744765111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/aff517ada6ef60c5c7b80909ef3afd88.avif?t=1744765111\" width=616 height=88 /></span>The puzzles and hidden objects are more than just challenges; they’re pieces of Ava’s journey. The game’s visuals, inspired by color theory and abstract art, react to the music, creating a beautiful, dynamic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find hidden areas and secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Piece together Ava's fragmented memories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Watch the environment change with the music</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/30364ba704df6089ad1a535a406e8f4f.poster.avif?t=1744765111\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384970/extras/30364ba704df6089ad1a535a406e8f4f.webm?t=1744765111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
